Interface LogToFileType

All Superinterfaces:

LogToFileTypeImpl
public interface LogToFileType
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Log To File Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Filename
  • Level
  • Selected
